    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/598450/extras/a8ad6f51a622191fc34c666bd08be4b4.avif?t=1724959213\" width=620 height=97 /></span><br><br><strong>Slice Dice &amp; Rice</strong> 是一款无血条的休闲格斗类独立游戏。本作创意来源于游戏《Bushido Blade》，游戏旨在于在对手的防御中找出破绽，使用干净利落的一击结束战斗。<br>冗烦的生命值系统？不存在的：每一次擦伤有可能打断你的攻击节奏，每一次看似无害的小伤都有可能要了你的命。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/598450/extras/d723c0077e300a63288e3ce9d95de677.avif?t=1724959213\" width=600 height=151 /></span><br><br><strong>游戏体验</strong><br>我们的目标是让每位玩家都能轻易上手。游戏内置了一套直观的基础能力系统，从而代替了难以记忆的按键组合，但同时保留了游戏必要的层次性与复杂性。玩家可通过佯装攻击以打断对手的移动，亦可以通过躲避或格挡以免受到攻击，攻击也可以用来抵挡对手的攻势。玩家在游戏中不仅需要格斗，更需要战术和策略。此乃武士之魂也！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/598450/extras/a9c0bde766153188ec9d447ebb7ed4ec.avif?t=1724959213\" width=600 height=141 /></span><br><br><strong>角色与场景</strong><br>玩家可以扮演八名角色中的一人进行游戏：每名角色都有他们独特故事的格斗风格。我们在游戏中添加了很多种不同的游戏体验，从独钟拳法、身轻如燕的得道高僧，到使用致命宝剑但行动缓慢的肌肉女，各种内容敬待你来体验。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/598450/extras/64645cf168435222a03ba9e3d8f0df32.avif?t=1724959213\" width=600 height=141 /></span><br><br>游戏场景设定在虚构的日本阴间，游戏内置6个手绘风格的独特关卡。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/598450/extras/806b4cb4c2dac6fece0365b9d34c84a5.avif?t=1724959213\" width=600 height=132 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/598450/extras/24df0100647d6b65f40e2e0bdeb187bd.avif?t=1724959213\" width=600 height=141 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/598450/extras/e2bedbda371e47ce41f8a81db57142b7.avif?t=1724959213\" width=600 height=151 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/598450/extras/aff670c696054f95270e8f405c269df9.avif?t=1724959213\" width=600 height=141 /></span>",
